description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Sussex Partnership is seeking to appoint a Specialty Doctor to the well-established Specialist Older Adults Mental Health Service in Brighton &amp; Hove. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Brighton &amp; Hove offers:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Journeys from coast to the countryside in minutes&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;A lifestyle with renowned cycle routes and picturesque walks, including the famous South Downs Way in the South Downs National Park&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;London is within easy reach via local/national bus routes and national mainline stations&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Easy access to airports - Gatwick and Heathrow are both within 90 minutes of the county, providing worldwide transport links&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Please note this post is being advertised internally as full-time (10PAs). Further information can be obtained from our Medical Staffing Team on 0300 304 0393.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;You will provide medical input and clinical leadership to the team and will be involved in the assessment and management of older adults who are experiencing a variety of mental health problems. You will work on wards at Mill View Hospital in Hove and as part of a friendly and supportive multi-disciplinary team which includes a consultant psychiatrist, doctors in training, a clinical psychologist, nurses and other allied health professionals.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We encourage applicants to visit our services and meet the team; please call to make a booking.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameScott CherryJob titleClinical DirectorEmail addressscott.cherry2@sussexpartnership.nhs.ukAdditional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Mandy Assin, Consultant Psychiatrist, &lt;em&gt;Specialist Older Adults Mental Health Service&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;mandy.assin@sussexpartnership.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
